pdate | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 11:49 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 11:49 UTC\\n\\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776167402491,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"3b9dc9ad\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check the sessions_list and compare against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_2ga6ztc99ehj_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"limit\": 20,\n                \"messageLimit\": 3\n              }\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_2ga6ztc99ehj_2\",\n              \"name\": \"read\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"path\": \"memory/heartbeat-state.json\"\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 430,\n            \"output\": 84,\n            \"totalTokens\": 14458,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          