       \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"HEARTBEAT_OK\\n\\n*QLHV group session (-5163901258) chỉ đang echo heartbeat, không có task thực. Pipeline healthy.*\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 826,\n            \"output\": 162,\n            \"totalTokens\": 145940,\n            \"cacheRead\": 143831,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 1121,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776166719638,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d5a4152722622bc8ee732381bbb32\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"56198dd5\",\n            \"seq\": 1267\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 11:46 UTC 14 Apr\\n\\nActive sessions: 2\\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (5p Progress Report): running — Ecosystem monitoring — ~3h 55m\\n• cron:6f3323ef (5p Progress Report - DTLX): running — DTLX ecosystem monitoring — ~1h 21m\\n\\nNotes:\\n• tg-group:-5163901258 (QLHV) only echoing heartbeat, no active tasks\\n• Lead direct session: done ✅\\n• Pipeline: HEALTHY ✅ | MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776167281634,\n          \"provenance\": {\n            \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n            \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\",\n            \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n          },\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"42c6c550\",\n            \"seq\": 1268\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Another heartbeat cron message. Pipeline is healthy, QLHV group is just echoing heartbeat, Lead direct is done. Nothing to act on.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"\\nHEARTBEAT_OK\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 37,\n            \"totalTokens\": 145534,\n            \"cacheRead\": 7391,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 138106,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776167281802,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d5c7358c3786dcd415f8ffe322904\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"b2e0f17a\",\n            \"seq\": 1269\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: Agent Status to Lead\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: Agent Status to Lead\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776167170108,\n      \"sessionId\": \"1711a8bf-82c6-4034-97c7-9d2b2e77e3c3\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 44713,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776161006770,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/1711a8bf-82c6-4034-97c7-9d2b2e77e3c3.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me analyze the sessions to compile a status report. I need to find ACTIVE master-orchestrator sessions, excluding the current cron session.\\n\\nLooking at the sessions list:\\n\\n1. **This cron session**: `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e` - running (EXCLUDE)\\n\\n2. **main heartbeat**: `agent:master-orchestrator:main` - status: done\\n\\n3. **DTLX 5p cron**: `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31` - status: running, startedAt: 1776152701090 (~10:25 UTC), label: \\\"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\\\"\\n   \\nI'm seeing a few more cron sessions here — the QLHV 5p Progress Report cron and another Telegram cron for sending messages, both currently running. I should filter these to focus on what I'm actually looking for.\\n\\nNow I'm narrowing down to the master-orchestrator agent sessions specifically. Looking at the active ones: the DTLX 5p cron has been running for about an hour and twenty minutes, while the QLHV 5p cron has been going for nearly four hours. There's also a Telegram delivery cron that's been running for nearly three hours but appears stuck on an exec command.\\n\\nThe other sessions are done or completed — the main heartbeat finished quickly, the Lead direct session ran for about two minutes, and the QLHV group session has been done for around thirty minutes despite still showing as running. There are also a couple of child subagents from the Lead session that have timed out or failed, along with some older cron sessions from earlier today.\\n\\nLooking at the current status, I can see that the two 5p progress report crons are the only truly active sessions — the DTLX one has been running for about an hour and twenty minutes, while the QLHV one has been active for nearly four hours. The QLHV group is just echoing heartbeat responses with no active work happening. Everything else is either completed, stuck, or timed out, so the system is essentially in a stable but idle state with just these two cron jobs maintaining watch.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \