liveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776167403003,"sessionId":"0e00b2c7-2d2a-4cc1-bdad-e74b3f12608a","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44559,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776167402492,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/0e00b2c7-2d2a-4cc1-bdad-e74b3f12608a.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31 5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX/QLHV] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, task started/completed, blocker appeared), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 11:49 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 11:49 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776167402491,"__openclaw":{"id":"3b9dc9ad","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the sessions_list and compare against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ga6ztc99ehj_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":3}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ga6ztc99ehj_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":430,"output":84,"totalTokens":14458,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776167402641,"responseId":"062d5cecb33364ee8a5b861218dcc222","__openclaw":{"id":"8577e0f6","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776167295038,"sessionId":"79d991d2-86b0-441a-845e-5006b442e8da","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":39572,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776154374281,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/79d991d2-86b0-441a-845e-5006b442e8da.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compare the current state vs the stored heartbeat state.\n\n**Stored State (11:44 UTC):**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` (5p Progress Report): running, lastSeen 11:38 UTC\n- `cron:6f3323ef` (5p Progress Report - DTLX): running, lastSeen 11:44 UTC\n- `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status to Lead): running, lastSeen 11:39 UTC\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` (QLHV Ecosystem Group): running, lastSeen 11:36 UTC, note: echo only\n\n\n- `telegram:group:-5168104492` (DTLX Ecosystem Group): done, ended 10:55 UTC\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` (Lead Direct Session): done, ended 10:42 UTC\n- `main` (Heartbeat Session): done, ended 11:15 UTC\n\nLooking at the current sessions as of 11:48 UTC, I can see the cron jobs are still active and the heartbeat session has ended as expected. The DTLX and Lead sessions have completed their work, and I'm noting the subagent sessions that are still running.\n\nChecking the state changes now, I notice the 5p Progress Report cron session has been actively running and consuming tokens since the last heartbeat, while the other cron jobs have maintained their running status. The telegram groups and direct messages are in their expected states.\n\nLooking at the DTLX progress report cron specifically, it's marked as running with a recent update timestamp, which suggests it's actively processing the DTLX monitoring work. Now I'm checking the QLHV Ecosystem Group session to see its current status. The DTLX group is confirmed done with no changes, and I'm seeing several subagents in failed or timeout states — mostly related to Telegram provider issues with the TroLy model, plus one killed and one orphaned session. There are also a couple of older cron sessions that haven't been active in hours, one of which is completely silent.\n\nThe stale Telegram delivery cron is still running but appears stuck on execution attempts from over an hour ago, and it's been marked in the previous heartbeat as a background issue that hasn't resolved itself yet.\n\nI'm checking the updatedAt timestamps to see if there's been any recent activity, but the timestamp for that cron session doesn't align with expected patterns—it's showing an earlier time than what I tracked before, which suggests the state file might be outdated or there's some inconsistency in how the timestamps are being recorded.\n\nRegardless, the status is still \"running\" and there's no heartbeat message in the most recent logs, so this stale cron session has been persisting across multiple check cycles without any change. The two active cron sessions remain stable, the QLHV group is still just echoing heartbeats with nothing substantive happening, and there are no new blockers or failures to report—the pipeline continues to function normally.\n\nNow I'm wondering if I should send the report to the QLHV group instead of staying silent, but looking back at the previous cycle, the same heartbeat state was already logged with a silent exit, so there's no actual change to report.\n\nThe cron sessions are still actively running with no new failures or blockers, so I'll update the heartbeat state and exit quietly."},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing current state against `heartbeat-state.json` (last: 11:44 UTC):\n\n**Sessions — no changes:**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ running (active in this session, lastSeen 11:38 UTC)\n- `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ running (active, updatedAt 11:44 UTC)\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ running\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` ✅ running (echo heartbeat only, no tasks — same as last cycle)\n- `telegram:group:-5168104492` ✅ done (same)\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` ✅ done (same)\n- `main` ✅ done (same)\n\n**Subagents:** 5 failed/timeout subagents — all from the previous work cycle, unchanged.\n\n**Pipeline:** HEALTHY ✅ | No new failures | No blockers\n\nNo state change since the last report. Exiting silently.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hoa7vc86oupz_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/heartbeat-state.json","content":"{\n  \"lastHeartbeat\": \"2026-04-14T11:48:00Z\",\n  \"lastReport\": \"2026-04-14T11:48:00Z\",\n  \"lastReportDelivered\": false,\n  \"silentExit\": true,\n  \"sessions\": {\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T11:38:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T11:44:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Cron: Agent Status to Lead\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T11:39:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestr