{"type":"message","id":"1e792e66","parentId":"b62f2c6f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:50:30.747Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me compare the current state (11:49 UTC) against the stored state (last: 11:48 UTC).\n\n**Stored State (11:48 UTC):**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` (5p Progress Report): running, lastSeen 11:38 UTC\n- `cron:6f3323ef` (5p Progress Report - DTLX): running, lastSeen 11:44 UTC\n- `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status to Lead): running, lastSeen 11:39 UTC\n\n\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` (QLHV): running, lastSeen 11:36 UTC\n- `telegram:group:-5168104492` (DTLX): done\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` (Lead): done\n- `main`: done\n\nNow checking the current sessions as of 11:49 UTC: the cron:ed2d0b5d is still running but hasn't reported in the last few minutes, the DTLX cron is actively working with recent updates, the agent status cron shows recent activity, the QLHV group is still running, and the Lead direct session has completed.\n\nLooking at the remaining active sessions, the DTLX group finished earlier today around 10:55, the main heartbeat session ended around 11:15, and there are several older cron jobs and stale subagent sessions still lingering. Comparing this against the stored state, most sessions match up, though the main heartbeat session appears to have ended earlier than the last recorded state.\n\nChecking the updated timestamps for the running cron jobs—the DTLX report cron shows an update from 11:44, which is actually slightly earlier than the stored lastSeen time, suggesting a timing discrepancy rather than any actual change. Since none of the core sessions have genuinely changed state since the last report at 11:48 UTC, and the cron job timing shows a timestamp slightly before the recorded heartbeat, I'll update the heartbeat file and exit silently without sending any report.","thinkingSignature":"84e4bab5ee4e9c7c38fab3af22b6d85d88978dd6ec05033a85549fcf24b2e51c"},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing current sessions (11:49 UTC) against `heartbeat-state.json` (last: 11:48 UTC):\n\n**Stable — no state changes:**\n- `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p cron): running ✅ (updatedAt 11:44 UTC — within same cycle)\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` (5p Progress Report): running ✅ (lastSeen 11:38 UTC, still active)\n- `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status to Lead): running ✅\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` (QLHV): running — echo heartbeat only, no active tasks ✅\n- `telegram:group:-5168104492` (DTLX): done ✅ (same)\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` (Lead): done ✅ (same)\n- `main`: done ✅ (same)\n\nNo new failures, no blockers, no new sessions. Pipeline stable.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b5nsbenx2tvg_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/heartbeat-state.json","content":"{\n  \"lastHeartbeat\": \"2026-04-14T11:49:00Z\",\n  \"lastReport\": \"2026-04-14T11:48:00Z\",\n  \"lastReportDelivered\": false,\n  \"silentExit\": true,\n  \"sessions\": {\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T11:38:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T11:49:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Cron: Agent Status to Lead\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T11:39:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"QLHV Ecosystem Group\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T11:36:00Z\", \"note\": \"Echoing heartbeat only, no active tasks\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"label\": \"DTLX Ecosystem Group\", \"endedAt\": \"2026-04-14T10:55:00Z\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T10:55:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"label\": \"Lead Direct Session\", \"endedAt\": \"2026-04-14T10:42:00Z\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T10:42:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:main\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"label\": \"Heartbeat Session\", \"endedAt\": \"2026-04-14T11:15:00Z\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T11:15:00Z\" }\n  },\n  \"pipelineHealth\": \"healthy\",\n  \"blockers\": [],\n  \"alerts\": [],\n  \"changesThisCycle\": [],\n  \"stableSince\": \"2026-04-14T11:44:00Z\"\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":23831,"output":1280,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":409,"totalTokens":39464,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776167409960,"responseId":"062d5cf3cc3bbc261353dbd6ba50e4fe"}}
